General.Name: Pacgold Ltd
General.Description: Pacgold Limited operates as a gold exploration company in Australia. Its principal property is the Alice River gold project that comprises a portfolio of eight mining leases and five exploration permits located in the Alice River region of north Queensland. The company was formerly known as Alice River Resources Pty Ltd. and changed its name to Pacgold Limited in December 2020. Pacgold Limited was incorporated in 2019 and is based in Brisbane, Australia.
